request = tornado.httputil.HTTPServerRequest(method='POST', uri='/evaluate',
    version='HTTP/1.1', body=
    b'{"api_key":"","script":"return [x.upper() for x in _arg1]","data":{"_arg1":["Aaron Bergman"]}}'
    )
result = EvaluateHandler._request_to_result(request)
expected = '["AARON BERGMAN"]'
self.assertEqual(result, expected)
